        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class K extinguishers in Heritage District restaurant and bar kitchens — the most active F&B compliance zone in Gilbert</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Expired tags in high-turnover Santan Village restaurant spaces</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Heat-degraded dry chemical agent in extinguishers stored in outdoor or unventilated locations</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Mounting violations in new commercial construction where builders omit permanent extinguisher mounting hardware</span></div></div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">Gilbert Fire Prevention Contacts</h2>
